  <title>Cogl.UserDataDestroyCallback</title>
  <p>When associating private data with a <link xref="Cogl.Object"/> a callback can be
given which will be called either if the object is destroyed or if
<link xref="Cogl.Object.set_user_data"/> is called with NULL user_data for the
same key.</p>

